I... I want to become stronger. Truly... to the point where
I can protect everyone...

Hmm... I have some free time until it's time to go out.
Maybe I should tease Ryan a little...

It seems like she wants to say something, but she can't find
her voice...

Lunaroa... Since then, you haven't been able to speak. I
can't do anything, but... I want to at least be by your
side.

\SM[nod]\SE[3] Thank you very much for being my magic
teacher...! \SE[0] I had a really great experience!

\SE[10]We've become good friends with Ronoa-chan, haven't
we...! \SE[10]I have a feeling she's saying something like
I'm really grateful...!

\SE[13]Ah, no. \SE[13]This time, I was able to train my
muscles quite a bit. As a reflection, I realized the
weakness of my core, so I will make improving that my goal
for next time. \SE[13]That's what she said.

\SE[14] Huh?! If I receive training from Lunaroa-san, I can
train my muscles...!? \SE[13] Please! Teach me too! \SE[12]
I want to defeat that Penis Girl...!

\SE[3]We have a present for you two! Since we don't have
money... \SE[6]We can't prepare anything expensive though...

Lunaroa and Vega received flower decorations made of baby's
breath from the children!

\SE[3]Wow...! It's cute...! I'm really happy...!
\SE[3]But when did you make this...?

\SE[3]While we were practicing, Tita diligently made this
for us.
\SE[6]Ehehe... I was a little bored, so...

\SE[16]Ehehe... We're matching, right, Vega? Look, aren't
you happy too? \SE[15]Say that you're happy.
\SM[slidef]\SE[26]Come on, come on!

\SE[92]You're so annoying... you know that. \!\SE[7]But, the
flower decoration... I'm really happy. \.Thank you.

\SE[90] (But if Laura sees me wearing the same flower
decoration as this person... \SE[91] I can't just not wear
it, so what should I do...)

\SE[1]I'm here to intrude. \.Is it about time for you to
return?

\SE[5]Why... are Lunaroa and Vega wearing matching flower
decorations...? \SE[95]Huh... is that... \SE[93]the
reason...?

\SE[40]Luna, you cheater...! \SE[39]This, this ladies' man!
Cabbage roll girl!! \SE[40]A heartbreaker! Bedroom maniac!!
Don Juan!!!

\SE[3] (You have a rich vocabulary for insulting
cheaters...)

\SE[40]Luna, you idiot...!! \.I don't care anymore!
\!\SE[100]I'll live on my own!!

\SE[3]T-Thank you so much for today! \!\SE[6]If it's okay,
could you teach me again sometime...?

\SE[7]Oh, gladly. \SE[8]If Lunaroa gets tired of theory of
willpower and theory of mind, don't hesitate to reach out to
me.

\SE[0]I would love to take Professor Vega's class. Please
count me in for the next opportunity as well. \SE[0]Because.

\SE[32]Now it's teacher, huh... \!\SE[7]Hehe...\.I'll gladly
give you a lesson.

\SE[9]Wait, Laura! It's a misunderstanding...!!
\SE[29]Please listen to what I have to say...!!

\SE[102]No...!! Please... leave me alone...!! \SE[38]If I
see your face... my determination will waver...!!

\SE[79]D-Determination...!? \!\SE[24]Stop it!! Don't make
such a decision...!!

\SE[14]There's an opening... Lunaroa-sama...!! \SE[21]Ah...
slender waist... long hair... It's wonderful...!!

\SE[123]......!!! Wh-What are you doing, Tita...!! \SE[40]
Stop it!! Don't touch my Lunaroa...!

\SE[14]You made a decision earlier, didn't you...! \SE[13]If
that's the case, Lunaroa-sama doesn't belong to anyone...!

\SE[47]Ah... They're fighting over me... \!\SE[45]What is
this pleasure...? \!\SE[24]No...! Don't fight over me...!

The 'Mountain Path of Elmo Village' has been added to the
teleportation crystal!
